headline.print_headline: Martino Future Uncertain After Latest Barca Failure
headline.main: Martino Future Uncertain After Latest Barca Failure

lead_paragraph: The future of Barcelona coach Gerardo Martino was uncertain on Saturday after a 2-2 home draw with lowly Getafe all but ended the club's bid for a fifth La Liga title in six years.
